th preceded that in the Doppler shift\nwhich again preceded enhancement in the intensity. The observed results were\nqualitatively reproduced by 1-D hydrodynamic simulations where energy was\ndeposited at both the footpoints of a monolithic coronal loop that mimicked the\nARTBs identified in the observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Mar 2018 17:37:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 May 2018 12:12:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-07"}
