ified outflow candidates are excellent\ntargets for follow up studies to better understand very early phase of\nprotostellar evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Mar 2018 11:15:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-06"}
